.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH config 1  "config " 
.SH NAME
config \- Manage agent configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBconfig\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage agent configuration.
.PP
All settings are stored in the SQLite database. No config files.
.PP
Key settings: nanogpt.api_key     NanoGPT API key (required) nanogpt.model       LLM model (default: claude\-sonnet\-4\-20250514) nanogpt.base_url    API endpoint daemon.enabled      Run regind as persistent user service (true/false)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
config\-list(1)
List all settings and their current values
.TP
config\-get(1)
Get the value of a setting
.TP
config\-set(1)
Set a configuration value
.TP
config\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH EXTRA
EXAMPLES:
  regin config set nanogpt.api_key sk\-abc123
  regin config set nanogpt.model gpt\-4o
  regin config set daemon.enabled true
  regin config get nanogpt.model
  regin config list
